# DaKanji custom SQLite builds

This folder contains the sources and scripts to build the custom SQLite version for DaKanji.

## Building

A general build script can be invoked using

```
TOOD: ADD
```

Each platform needs slightly different build steps.
Therefore, the below sections explain the steps for each platform

### MacOS

1. Create `sqlite-vec.h`

```bash
cd sqlite-vec
make sqlite-vec.h
```

2. Compile the static CR-SQLite

```bash
cd cr-sqlite/core/
make static
cd ../..
```

3. Build the shell / dylib
   
```bash
make # builds shell and dylib
make shell # builds only shell
make dylib # builds only dylib
```

