## Updating sources

### [Amalgamation](https://www.sqlite.org/amalgamation.html)

Download the full archive and extract it in this directory (`custom_sqlite`).
The build script ignores the version number.
The name must follow this scheme `sqlite-amalgamation-xxx`

### [SQLite mirror for extensions](https://github.com/sqlite/sqlite)

The build scripts expect the extensions to be in `custom_sqlite/ext/misc` same as in the original repo.

### [SQLite-vec](https://github.com/asg017/sqlite-vec)

This is included as a submodule, just switch to the branch, commit, tag you want.

### [CR-SQLite](https://github.com/vlcn-io/cr-sqlite)

This is included as a submodule, just switch to the branch, commit, tag you want.
